seeds_list.sentence: He was quiet.
No he was rather quiet after you left.
Yes he felt like talking a lot.
I heard that he didn't like that place.
I didn't hear what she said to him.
Did you hear what he wanted to grow?
No nobody told me.
Yes I heard that he wanted to grow tomatoes.
I saw several horses on the road.
I didn't see anyone that I knew.
I went to see a film on Wednesday.
Did you see what she was trying to create?
It was beautiful.
Yes I thought it was very beautiful.
No I didn't know what she was doing.
I didn't go anywhere last month.
Did you go anywhere in the world last year?
No I didn't have enough money for holidays.
Yes I was lucky enough to travel to Africa.
I asked what she wanted to include.
